contentrichtext.text: {{Other uses of|Kosovo}} {{Orphan|date=August 2008|att=March 2013}} {{Coord|59|18|00|N|040|43|00|E|display=title}} '''Kosovo''' ({{Lang-ru|Ко́сово}}) is a [[types of settlements in Russia|village]] in [[Mezhdurechensky District, Vologda Oblast|Mezhdurechensky District]] of [[Vologda Oblast]], [[Russia]]. [[subdivisions of Russia#Administrative divisions|Administratively]], it belongs to Nozemsky Selsoviet.<ref name="OKATO">{{OKATO reference|19 232 816 008}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ocato.ru/okato.php?code=19232816&vid=2|title=Код ОКАТО: 19 232 816 000|publisher=ocato.ru|language=Russian|accessdate=11 October 2011}}</ref> ==References== {{reflist}} [[Category:Rural localities in Vologda Oblast]] {{VologdaOblast-geo-stub}}
